程序包 org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.cassandra

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CassandraCommitter
    CheckpointCommitter that saves information about completed checkpoints within a separate table in a cassandra database.
    CassandraPojoSink<IN>
    Flink Sink to save data into a Cassandra cluster using Mapper, which it uses annotations from com.datastax.driver.mapping.
    CassandraSink<IN>
    This class wraps different Cassandra sink implementations to provide a common interface for all of them.
    CassandraSink.CassandraPojoSinkBuilder<IN>  
    CassandraSink.CassandraSinkBuilder<IN>  
    CassandraSink.CassandraTupleSinkBuilder<IN extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple>  
    CassandraSinkBase<IN,V>
    CassandraSinkBase is the common abstract class of CassandraPojoSink and CassandraTupleSink.
    CassandraTupleSink<IN extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple>
    Flink Sink to save data into a Cassandra cluster.
    CassandraTupleWriteAheadSink<IN extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple>
    Sink that emits its input elements into a Cassandra database.
    ClusterBuilder
    This class is used to configure a Cluster after deployment.
